reviewText: i love the mob and gangsters so i have a large collection ,but these tapes from ROGUES GALLERY is by far the best of my collection.they give you details about the different gangsters that even i had never saw or heard of before.not just a lot of old pics and a couple of guys talking but actual and videos of their homelife and children.a must have for any fan of this type of genre.if anyone knows if there are more than the eight i have and where to get them PLEASE SHARE THE INFO!!!I HAVE luciano,lansky,seigel,mickey cohen,dillinger,bonnie&clyde,giancana.
